<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Password Reset</title></head>
<body style="font-family:sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px">
  <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
  <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
  <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the link below to set a new password:</p>
  <p><a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="background:#2563EB;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block">Reset Password</a></p>
  <p>This link expires in <strong>1 hour</strong>. If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
  <p>— The CRM Team</p>
</body>
</html>
